{
  "stem": "22447.4",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's a difficult question to answer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some people believe in it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Other people don't believe in anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A person that will say, if they say they don't believe in anything, you can't blame them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When you've got a wife and children, or all your family wiped out, they all say, where, where was your God?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You see, it says.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's written somewhere, that God instructed Abraham to kill his son.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And just as he's about to kill him, he told him to stop.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So it says, from that day, they work out that it was God's command he should kill his son.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he was quite willing to do it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this was God's command that this should happen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But it was Reverend [INAUDIBLE]-- I think it was Reverend [INAUDIBLE] who said it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He  said, whether it's God's command or not, we're not going to let these people as they are.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We're going to do everything we can to save them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As I said, I had a cousin in Paris.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And about a year after we come back, we went to see him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she had come from Poland through Germany into France.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She had an aunt and uncle.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She found an aunt that got married.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She also lost a, a husband and children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he lost all his family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they got married in Germany.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were living in Paris.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we want to see them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's how we met.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I said-- well, there's not much-- of course, they were in Paris.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the working conditions were difficult.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They couldn't speak the language.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They'd gone there with nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I said, well, if you come over to  London, so at least you've got a base or something.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
